column7: Description

Fun board game for 2-4 players that involves risk, deduction, and luck. The goal of the game is to get your love letter to the princess. I no longer play this game anymore which is why I am looking to sell it.
This elegant and simple design features, only 16 cards but hours of fun!
Contents: 1 Rulebook, 16 game cards, 4 reference cards, 13 tokens of affection
20 minutes playtime

Great gaming mouse that has been used for about 6 months. Kept in really good condition with no scratches. I bought a new vertical mouse so I have no need for this mouse anymore. USed it to play many different video games and has never let me down.
Hero 16K Sensor: Logitech's most accurate sensor yet with upto 16,000 DPI and 10X the power efficiency of previous generation
Ergonomic Ambidextrous Design: Tournament ready mouse developed with esports pros for maximum comfort, control and 50 million click durability
Ultra Lightweight: Innovative endoskeleton design creates a super thin yet incredibly strong outer shell

I bought this bicycle for my son a year ago. It was rarely used, and overtime, I realized that we no longer need it. The bicycle looks like new and it works without any issues. The bicycle has support wheels, a small pocket to carry stuff, an adjustable seat, and it applies breaks with rear paddling. This bicycle is for kids with age between 5 and 7.

Apple keyboard with numeric keypad (wireless, rechargeable). Keyboard uses wireless and bluetooth; compatible with any mac laptop or computer, charges with lightning cable. Condition is used, but excellent; all keys work without any issues. Accompanying charging / lightning cable not provided.
-Has numeric keypad, with page up / page down buttons
-Bluetooth connection to any Mac device (not sure if it works with windows systems)
-All keys functional

column4: VTECH Sit to Stand Learning Walker
column7:
This walker has easy-to-remove activity panel is great for floor play and is packed with features and the legs fold for easy storage. Five light-up piano keys introduce colors and numbers, while spinning gears help develop fine motor skills. Attach the panel to the adjustable two-speed walker as little ones grow, and watch them go! Intended for ages 9-36 months. Requires 2 AA batteries and the batteries are included. 
•  Electronic play panel can be removed from the walker for floor play
•  Attach and detach the cell phone to trigger playful phrases, sounds and a cute song
•  Speed control on the wheels helps keep beginner walkers at a slower pace

This table-chair are for kids under age 7 years. The height of both table and chairs is adjustable. There are some scratches on one of the chairs, but except that the condition is excellent. It comes with four chairs of similar design and color as shown in the picture.
 
•                    STURDY DURABLE TODDLER TABLE AND CHAIR SET: Chairs weight capacity: 220 lbs, Table weight capacity: 220 lbs
•                    HEIGHT ADJUSTABLE DESK & SEAT: There are 5 levels for table to adjust from 18.9”-23.6”, 3 level for chairs to adjust from 20.8”-22.4”.
•                    47” tabletop size, suits boys and girls of 2 years-10 years old, 1" adjustable table pad solve the problem of uneven ground effectively; inclined legs prevent children from flipping while playing games.

column4: VTECH Sit to Stand Learning Walker
column7:
This walker has easy-to-remove activity panel is great for floor play and is packed with features and the legs fold for easy storage. Five light-up piano keys introduce colors and numbers, while spinning gears help develop fine motor skills. Attach the panel to the adjustable two-speed walker as little ones grow, and watch them go! Intended for ages 9-36 months. Requires 2 AA batteries and the batteries are included. 
•                    Electronic play panel can be removed from the walker for floor play
•                    Attach and detach the cell phone to trigger playful phrases, sounds and a cute song
•                    Speed control on the wheels helps keep beginner walkers at a slower pace
